sermon have we all been hit by triple blindness the blindenss 
of the eye the blindness of the heart and the blindness of the 
conscience 
how can we be blind to the sight of homeless families taking 
shelter in forests 
the newround of fullscale warfare broke out at dawn friday 
between aouns 19000 army troops and the 6000 militiamen of 
geageas lebanese forces shattering a march 3 ceasefire that had 
been threatened by sporadic clashes for weeks 
the casualties in the two days of clashes brought the overall 
